*.pkl

# Trained models: ship the ones scoring actually loads, so a fresh clone can
# run the platform without a 10-20 minute training pass. The per-family
# candidates stay out — `demand-champion-{h}` is a byte-identical copy of
# whichever family won, so committing both would double the weight for nothing,
# and the losing candidates' metrics are already recorded in `model_runs`.
*.joblib
!ml/artifacts/demand-champion-*.joblib
!ml/artifacts/shortage.joblib

